  "legend": "While the Deredeo Dreadnought shares many core systems with the famed Contemptor class, it was expressly designed as a heavy weapons platform, combining superior firepower with the flexibility of a walker. Now rare, Deredeos are treasured assets whose survivability and killing power have proved decisive on countless battlefields.",
